title: Bunkercast XXXII: Pressure Points & My best friend is a brick
itunes:title: Bunkercast XXXII: Pressure Points & My best friend is a brick
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal bring you the latest news in the NFL including Winston heading to the Saints and Brett Farve anticipating Aaron Rodgers playing somewhere else. The heroes take you through teams and players that have a lot of pressure on them in the upcoming season.
